            "title": "Fission-fusion bat behavior as a strategy for balancing the conflicting needs of maximizing information accuracy and minimizing infection risk",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Kazutaka",
                    "lastName": "Kashima"
