            "title": "Analyzing NEXRAD doppler radar images to assess nightly dispersal patterns and population trends in Brazilian free-tailed bats (Tadarida brasiliensis)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "J. W.",
                    "lastName": "Horn"
